'''黎凡特公司'''（{{lang-en|'''Levant Company'''}}或{{lang|en|'''Company of Turkey Merchants'''}}）是一家英格蘭[[特許公司|特許公司]]。

==历史==
1592年由[[威尼斯公司|威尼斯公司]]（Venice Company）和土耳其公司（Turkey Company）合併而來，特許狀則由[[伊麗莎白一世|伊麗莎白一世]]頒發<ref name="autogenerated1964">Kenneth R. Andrews (1964), Elizabethan Privateering 1583–1603, Cambridge University Press</ref>。成立該公司目的是維持和運營英格蘭與[[奧斯曼帝國|奧斯曼帝國]][[黎凡特|黎凡特]]地區的商業業務。直到1825年該公司才解體。<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.historytoday.com/james-mather/turkey-merchants |title=The Turkey Merchants |last1=Mather |first1=James |last2= |first2= |date=May 2011 |journal=History Today |volume=61 |issue=5 |publisher= |access-date= |quote= |archive-date=2016-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911070822/http://www.historytoday.com/james-mather/turkey-merchants |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.historytoday.com/sarah-searight/turkey-merchants-life-levant-company |title=The Turkey Merchants: Life in the Levant Company |last1=Searight |first1=Sarah |last2= |first2= |date=June 1966 |journal=History Today |volume=16 |issue=6 |publisher= |access-date= |quote= |archive-date=2016-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911081035/http://www.historytoday.com/sarah-searight/turkey-merchants-life-levant-company |dead-url=no }}</ref>

